sig_info: Venompool begins each Quest with 1 Persistent Charge, which he can spend in the Pre-Fight Menu to select one Blender Buff as his Fav Food for the next fight. The Fav Food is more likely to be chosen at random and gains +5 to 50% Potency.
Each time Venompool enters a fight, he gains his Persistent Charge back.
